graph LR
    subgraph "User Interface"
        Modal[Test Detail Modal<br/>Shows error logs]
        Display[AI Analysis Display<br/>Root Cause<br/>Component<br/>Confidence: 95%<br/>Evidence<br/>Suggested Action]
    end

    subgraph "Backend"
        API[Flask API<br/>/api/analyze-failure]
        Analyzer[AI Analyzer<br/>analyzer.py]
    end

    subgraph "Data Storage"
        DB[(Database<br/>ai_analyses table<br/>Cached results)]
    end

    subgraph "External AI Service"
        Vertex[Google Vertex AI<br/>Claude Sonnet 4<br/>Model: claude-sonnet-4<br/>Region: us-east5]
    end

    Modal -->|Auto-load on open| DB
    DB -->|Existing analysis| Display

    Modal -->|Fresh analysis needed| API
    API --> Analyzer
    Analyzer -->|Send:<br/>Test name<br/>Error message<br/>Logs 3000 chars<br/>Platform<br/>Version| Vertex

    Vertex -->|Return:<br/>Root cause<br/>Component<br/>Confidence<br/>Failure type<br/>Evidence<br/>Suggested action| Analyzer

    Analyzer --> DB
    DB --> Display
    Display --> Modal

    Note1[Auto-loads from cache<br/>No button needed]
    Note2[Cost: $0.024 per analysis<br/>Cached permanently]

    style DB fill:#99ccff
    style Vertex fill:#ffccff
    style Display fill:#ccffcc
    style Modal fill:#ffcc99
